arch sage
name old priest
msg
@match gorokh
We worship Gorokh, our master, and we
seek redemption in Hell.

@match yes
@cond $who->contr->peaceful
@eval $who->contr->peaceful (0)
You are a brave adventurer! You can now go out and
cause harm and please our God, Gorokh!

@match yes
Don't chatter, Gorokh demands that you go out and slaughter some people!

H<You can now kill other hostile players and steal from them. Talk to the
priest of Valriel in Scorn to change this>

@match *
@cond $who->contr->peaceful
Ha! A pacifist! A weakling!

You maggot! If you were worth just half of our lowest follower you'd
go out and slaughter some people like in the good old times!

If you want to prove yourself in the path of evil and fun, say yes!

H<Saying yes will change your alignment from peaceful to hostile, allowing
you to kill other hostile players (or get killed), steal from them (or be stolen from)
and generally do nasty things>

@match *
Welcome to the temple of Gorokh!

Our master Gorokh is very pleased with the path you have chosen!
endmsg
hp 99999
maxhp 99999
